## 🎨 Global Image Specifications

To ensure the portfolio grid and sliding animations render seamlessly, all screenshots must match these specifications:

| Metric | Target Specification | Rationale |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Aspect Ratio** | **8:5 (or 16:10)** | Matches the GSAP layout scaling box (`width: 2400` by `height: 1500`) |
| **Resolution** | **2400 × 1500 px** | Ensures sharp details on high-DPI retina displays |
| **Format** | **Lossless PNG** | Keeps typography and boundaries crisp without compression artifacts |
| **Theme Aesthetic** | **Dark Mode** (where applicable) | Complements the portfolio's deep cybernetic styling and custom accent colors |
| **Data Quality** | **Populated & Active** | Never capture empty states. Run test commands to populate history logs |

